params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD as ITEM_CD, " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_NAME as ITEM_NAME, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD as PROC_COST_CLS_CD, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_CLS_NAME as PROC_COST_CLS_NAME, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.CLASIFICATION_CD as CLASIFICATION_CD, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ONEROUS_CONS_FLG as ONEROUS_CONS_FLG_DN, " +" M_HOME_CUR.CUR_UNIT as HOME_CUR_UNIT, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_01) as PROC_COST_01, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_02) as PROC_COST_02, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_03) as PROC_COST_03, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_04) as PROC_COST_04, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_05) as PROC_COST_05, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_06) as PROC_COST_06, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_07) as PROC_COST_07, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_08) as PROC_COST_08, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_09) as PROC_COST_09, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_10) as PROC_COST_10, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_11) as PROC_COST_11, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_12) as PROC_COST_12, " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_SUM) as PROC_COST_SUM, " +" to_char(M_ITEM_PROC_COST.MODIFY_COUNT) as MODIFY_COUNT " +"from " +" M_PROC_COST, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST, " +" M_ITEM, " +" SYS_HOME_CUR, " +" M_CUR M_HOME_CUR " +"where " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST_CLS.PLANT_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_CLS_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD " +" and SYS_HOME_CUR.CTRL_CD(+) = 'SYSTEM' " +" and M_HOME_CUR.CUR_CD(+) = SYS_HOME_CUR.HOME_CUR_CD " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.YEAR(+) = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.HALF_TERM_TYP(+) = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.COST_TYP(+) = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD LIKE ? " +"order by " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD"

"select " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD as ITEM_CD, " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_NAME as ITEM_NAME, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD as PROC_COST_CLS_CD, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_CLS_NAME as PROC_COST_CLS_NAME, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.CLASIFICATION_CD as CLASIFICATION_CD, " +" to_char(M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ONEROUS_CONS_FLG) as ONEROUS_CONS_FLG, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_UNIT_QTY, 1)) as PROC_COST_UNIT_QTY, " +" M_PROC_COST.STOCK_UNIT as STOCK_UNIT, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_01, 0)) as PROC_COST_01, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_02, 0)) as PROC_COST_02, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_03, 0)) as PROC_COST_03, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_04, 0)) as PROC_COST_04, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_05, 0)) as PROC_COST_05, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_06, 0)) as PROC_COST_06, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_07, 0)) as PROC_COST_07, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_08, 0)) as PROC_COST_08, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_09, 0)) as PROC_COST_09, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_10, 0)) as PROC_COST_10, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_11, 0)) as PROC_COST_11, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_12, 0)) as PROC_COST_12, " +" to_char(nvl(M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_SUM, 0)) as PROC_COST_SUM, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_01_NAME as PROC_COST_01_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_02_NAME as PROC_COST_02_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_03_NAME as PROC_COST_03_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_04_NAME as PROC_COST_04_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_05_NAME as PROC_COST_05_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_06_NAME as PROC_COST_06_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_07_NAME as PROC_COST_07_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_08_NAME as PROC_COST_08_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_09_NAME as PROC_COST_09_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_10_NAME as PROC_COST_10_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_11_NAME as PROC_COST_11_NAME, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_12_NAME as PROC_COST_12_NAME, " +" to_char(M_ITEM_PROC_COST.MODIFY_COUNT) as MODIFY_COUNT " +"from " +" M_PROC_COST, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST, " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.PLANT_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_CLS_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD " +" and M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.YEAR(+) = to_number(?) " +" and M_PROC_COST.HALF_TERM_TYP(+) = to_number(?) " +" and M_PROC_COST.COST_TYP(+) = to_number(?) " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD = ?"

"select " +" to_char(M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST " +"where " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PROC_COST_CLS_CD\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"

"select " +" to_char(M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST " +"where " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PROC_COST_CLS_CD\\" = ?"

"update " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST " +"set " +" \\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ONEROUS_CONS_FLG\\" = to_number(?) " +"where " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PROC_COST_CLS_CD\\" = ?"

"delete from " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST " +"where " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PROC_COST_CLS_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST " +"where " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" <> ?"

"select " +" M_CS_PROC.\\"CS_PROC_NAME\\" as \\"CS_PROC_NAME\\", " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.\\"DEL_FLG\\") as \\"DEL_FLG\\" " +"from " +" M_CS_PROC " +"where " +" M_CS_PROC.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.\\"PROC_COST_CLS_NAME\\" as \\"PROC_COST_CLS_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS " +"where " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST_CLS.\\"PROC_COST_CLS_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" to_char(M_PROC_COST.\\"DEL_FLG\\") as \\"DEL_FLG\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_COST " +"where " +" M_PROC_COST.\\"YEAR\\" = to_number(?) " +" and M_PROC_COST.\\"HALF_TERM_TYP\\" = to_number(?) " +" and M_PROC_COST.\\"COST_TYP\\" = to_number(?) " +" and M_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.\\"PROC_COST_CLS_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\" as \\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_HOME_CUR.CUR_UNIT as HOME_CUR_UNIT " +"from " +" SYS_HOME_CUR, " +" M_CUR M_HOME_CUR " +"where " +" SYS_HOME_CUR.CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" and M_HOME_CUR.CUR_CD = SYS_HOME_CUR.HOME_CUR_CD"

"select " +" COUNT(1) " +"from " +" M_PROC_COST, " +" M_PROC_COST_CLS, " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST, " +" M_ITEM, " +" SYS_HOME_CUR, " +" M_CUR M_HOME_CUR " +"where " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST_CLS.PLANT_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST_CLS.PROC_COST_CLS_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD " +" and M_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD(+) = M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PROC_COST_CLS_CD " +" and SYS_HOME_CUR.CTRL_CD(+) = 'SYSTEM' " +" and M_HOME_CUR.CUR_CD(+) = SYS_HOME_CUR.HOME_CUR_CD " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.YEAR(+) = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.HALF_TERM_TYP(+) = ? " +" and M_PROC_COST.COST_TYP(+) = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.CS_PROC_CD = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.ITEM_CD LIKE ? " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"
